          "email": "pfarrell@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2025-09-04 23:38:44.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-0000 utils: allow stripe size on EC parity components",
        "message": "LU-0000 utils: allow stripe size on EC parity components\n\nDrop the parity guard in layout_stripe_size_set() so parity\ncomponents can inherit and accept stripe-size values, while\nstill forbidding it for foreign layout pattern.\n\ntests: sanity-ec: assert parity stripe size when -S is used\n\nAdd optional expected stripe size to verify_ec_layout() and\nuse it in 3c (4+2, -S 1M) to check both data and parity stripe\nsizes via getstripe.\n\nTest-Parameters: forjanitoronly\nSigned-off-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I14bd75a0aa6f735290c0523cbe4b115b000dd0f0\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
